headline: Palantir Stock Is Up 1,000% in the Last 3 Years. Can It Hit $1 Trillion by 2030?
summary: Palantir delivered another blowout earnings report with revenue growth accelerating to 39%.  The stock pulled back due to pressure from its valuation, which includes a price-to-sales ratio of more than 80.  The size of its addressable market is unclear, but will be a key determinant of its future.
